SOBERAY
v.
GREYHOUND LINES, INC. 2019-0722 Supreme Court of Ohio. July 8, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On motion for admission pro hac vice of Conor T. Fitzpatrick. Motion granted. Pursuant to Gov.Bar R. XII(4), counsel shall file a notice of permission to appear pro hac vice with the Supreme Court's Office of Attorney Services within 30 days.
